00:01:00.460 --> 00:01:02.290 align:middle line:84%
We are, first and
foremost, a spirit

00:01:02.290 --> 00:01:05.200 align:middle line:84%
encompassing this
body, this human body.

00:01:05.200 --> 00:01:09.270 align:middle line:84%
It really is the overcoat,
if you will, of our spirit.

00:01:09.270 --> 00:01:10.540 align:middle line:90%
And the spirit never dies.

00:01:10.540 --> 00:01:13.800 align:middle line:84%
The spirit just leaves the body
and goes on to another level.

00:01:13.800 --> 00:01:16.660 align:middle line:84%
So when people talk about
death, there really is no death.

00:01:16.660 --> 00:01:18.510 align:middle line:84%
The two biggest
illusions we have

00:01:18.510 --> 00:01:20.500 align:middle line:84%
in the three-dimensional
world-- number one

00:01:20.500 --> 00:01:23.160 align:middle line:84%
is the sense that there's
death, which there is not.

00:01:23.160 --> 00:01:24.400 align:middle line:90%
You cannot kill energy.

00:01:24.400 --> 00:01:26.140 align:middle line:90%
Energy changes form.

00:01:26.140 --> 00:01:28.569 align:middle line:84%
And the other is a sense
of separativeness--

00:01:28.569 --> 00:01:30.110 align:middle line:84%
that we're separate
from one another,

00:01:30.110 --> 00:01:32.150 align:middle line:90%
when, in reality, we're all one.

00:01:32.150 --> 00:01:34.920 align:middle line:84%
We are well-connected
as that oneness--

00:01:34.920 --> 00:01:36.170 align:middle line:90%
the oneness, the greatness.

00:01:36.170 --> 00:01:38.700 align:middle line:84%
And I do believe from my many,
many years of communicating

00:01:38.700 --> 00:01:41.630 align:middle line:84%
with the spiritual realms
that when we first pass over

00:01:41.630 --> 00:01:44.050 align:middle line:84%
to the other side of life,
we have an awareness, number

00:01:44.050 --> 00:01:46.620 align:middle line:84%
one, that we are, indeed,
alive-- very much alive.

00:01:46.620 --> 00:01:50.480 align:middle line:84%
We're actually more alive out
of the body than in the body.

00:01:50.480 --> 00:01:54.760 align:middle line:84%
And spirit people refer
to us as the walking dead.

00:01:54.760 --> 00:01:55.500 align:middle line:90%
Is that funny?

00:01:55.500 --> 00:01:56.970 align:middle line:90%
The walking dead.

00:01:56.970 --> 00:01:58.680 align:middle line:84%
Because it seems that,
in the human body,

00:01:58.680 --> 00:02:01.500 align:middle line:84%
we're very, very concerned with
everything 9:00 to 5:00-- what

00:02:01.500 --> 00:02:03.000 align:middle line:84%
happens in front
of us, what's going

00:02:03.000 --> 00:02:05.770 align:middle line:84%
to happen with the
rest of the day, what's

00:02:05.770 --> 00:02:08.014 align:middle line:84%
going to happen with
our money and family,

00:02:08.014 --> 00:02:09.389 align:middle line:84%
and where are we
going from here?

00:02:09.389 --> 00:02:12.394 align:middle line:84%
And we live kind of in a
fear-based kind of motivation.

00:02:12.394 --> 00:02:13.810 align:middle line:84%
And I've got to
tell you that when

00:02:13.810 --> 00:02:15.935 align:middle line:84%
you leave the body, the
awareness that you have is,

00:02:15.935 --> 00:02:16.670 align:middle line:90%
wow.

00:02:16.670 --> 00:02:19.820 align:middle line:84%
I no longer am heavied by
this body, no longer burdened

00:02:19.820 --> 00:02:22.510 align:middle line:90%
by the body, and I'm so free.

00:02:22.510 --> 00:02:25.500 align:middle line:90%
I feel so incredibly alive.

00:02:25.500 --> 00:02:27.880 align:middle line:84%
And I remember when I was in
the confines of that body,

00:02:27.880 --> 00:02:29.330 align:middle line:90%
I felt like I wasn't alive.

00:02:29.330 --> 00:02:31.630 align:middle line:84%
And spirit people
often say that.

00:02:31.630 --> 00:02:35.106 align:middle line:84%
Spirit people often say that
you need to take time every once

00:02:35.106 --> 00:02:36.770 align:middle line:84%
and a while and
focus on yourself,

00:02:36.770 --> 00:02:39.574 align:middle line:84%
be centered with yourself, and
connect with everybody else.

00:02:39.574 --> 00:02:40.990 align:middle line:84%
The second greatest
illusion there

00:02:40.990 --> 00:02:43.519 align:middle line:84%
is a sense of
separativeness-- that we're

00:02:43.519 --> 00:02:45.560 align:middle line:84%
separate from one another
when, in reality, we're

00:02:45.560 --> 00:02:46.572 align:middle line:90%
all connected.

00:02:46.572 --> 00:02:48.530 align:middle line:84%
And when you pass over
to the spiritual realms,

00:02:48.530 --> 00:02:50.450 align:middle line:84%
you have the
awareness that you are

00:02:50.450 --> 00:02:52.780 align:middle line:84%
part of that person,
that person, that person,

00:02:52.780 --> 00:02:55.100 align:middle line:84%
and that we're all
connected, like a thread.

00:02:55.100 --> 00:02:57.260 align:middle line:84%
There's one big great
tapestry, and we're all

00:02:57.260 --> 00:02:59.410 align:middle line:90%
connected to each other.

00:02:59.410 --> 00:03:02.530 align:middle line:84%
It's a shame we don't realize
that while we're still

00:03:02.530 --> 00:03:04.300 align:middle line:90%
in the human body.

00:03:04.300 --> 00:03:08.600 align:middle line:84%
I think if we realized that,
that we were part of each other

00:03:08.600 --> 00:03:10.880 align:middle line:84%
and that what we
think about someone,

00:03:10.880 --> 00:03:13.720 align:middle line:84%
the words that are
expressed out of the mouth,

00:03:13.720 --> 00:03:16.840 align:middle line:84%
and these thoughts that we
have, the feelings that we have

00:03:16.840 --> 00:03:18.994 align:middle line:84%
that we portray to
somebody else-- boy,

00:03:18.994 --> 00:03:20.660 align:middle line:84%
if we could only see
what we did and how

00:03:20.660 --> 00:03:23.240 align:middle line:90%
it affected that person.

00:03:23.240 --> 00:03:25.240 align:middle line:84%
It's really not until
you go sometimes--

00:03:25.240 --> 00:03:27.031 align:middle line:84%
if you're not spiritually
aware when you're

00:03:27.031 --> 00:03:29.710 align:middle line:84%
walking in this human
body, unfortunately,

00:03:29.710 --> 00:03:32.270 align:middle line:84%
it's when you pass
away, when you die.

00:03:32.270 --> 00:03:34.270 align:middle line:84%
And I say it's a little
bit too late-- you know?

00:03:34.270 --> 00:03:35.930 align:middle line:90%
A little bit too late.

00:03:35.930 --> 00:03:38.380 align:middle line:84%
Because you have that
awareness too late,

00:03:38.380 --> 00:03:41.049 align:middle line:84%
when you're not in the
human, that, oh, wow.

00:03:41.049 --> 00:03:43.340 align:middle line:84%
And I've heard it from many
spirits who I've talked to.

00:03:43.340 --> 00:03:45.620 align:middle line:84%
"If only I knew then
what I know now,

00:03:45.620 --> 00:03:47.670 align:middle line:84%
I would have treated
people so differently.

00:03:47.670 --> 00:03:49.640 align:middle line:84%
I would have behaved
so differently.

00:03:49.640 --> 00:03:51.580 align:middle line:84%
I wouldn't have
said those things."

00:03:51.580 --> 00:03:53.900 align:middle line:84%
When you pass into
the spiritual realms,

00:03:53.900 --> 00:03:56.420 align:middle line:84%
you see the power
that words have.

00:03:56.420 --> 00:03:59.237 align:middle line:84%
You see the world
you left behind.

00:03:59.237 --> 00:04:01.570 align:middle line:84%
One of the first things that
happens after you pass over

00:04:01.570 --> 00:04:04.670 align:middle line:84%
is you have a life review where
you relive every single moment

00:04:04.670 --> 00:04:07.770 align:middle line:84%
you lived in the human body and
how your words, your thoughts

00:04:07.770 --> 00:04:10.170 align:middle line:84%
affected that person,
and that person,

00:04:10.170 --> 00:04:11.546 align:middle line:84%
and that person,
and that person.

00:04:11.546 --> 00:04:13.711 align:middle line:84%
And in the spiritual realms,
you've got to look back

00:04:13.711 --> 00:04:15.470 align:middle line:84%
and you have to try
to forgive yourself

00:04:15.470 --> 00:04:19.180 align:middle line:84%
for the power, the words, the
thoughts, the emotions you

00:04:19.180 --> 00:04:21.269 align:middle line:90%
left behind with other people.

00:04:21.269 --> 00:04:24.010 align:middle line:84%
What did you create
in the lifetime?

00:04:24.010 --> 00:04:26.610 align:middle line:84%
When you were given-- your
soul was given the opportunity

00:04:26.610 --> 00:04:28.860 align:middle line:84%
to walk upon the
Earth and to interact

00:04:28.860 --> 00:04:33.940 align:middle line:84%
with other human beings and
to share that aspect of love--

00:04:33.940 --> 00:04:35.310 align:middle line:90%
it's an incredible opportunity.

00:04:35.310 --> 00:04:37.020 align:middle line:90%
It's an incredible opportunity.

00:04:37.020 --> 00:04:40.840 align:middle line:84%
And I think it'd be much
more beneficial to have

00:04:40.840 --> 00:04:44.850 align:middle line:84%
that realization when you're
still in the body-- the power

00:04:44.850 --> 00:04:46.690 align:middle line:84%
that your words and
your thoughts have.

00:04:46.690 --> 00:04:50.890 align:middle line:84%
And if you'd be aware of
that, and the responsibility

00:04:50.890 --> 00:04:52.830 align:middle line:84%
