words, your thoughts,

00:04:52.830 --> 00:04:54.330 align:middle line:84%
your interactions
with other people,

00:04:54.330 --> 00:04:56.163 align:middle line:84%
I think you'd behave
very, very differently.

00:04:56.163 --> 00:04:57.420 align:middle line:90%
