00:06:34.180 --> 00:06:36.370 align:middle line:84%
And I say, yes,
but not necessarily

00:06:36.370 --> 00:06:38.380 align:middle line:90%
in the biblical traditions.

00:06:38.380 --> 00:06:41.720 align:middle line:84%
Heaven is really the
energy you've left behind.

00:06:41.720 --> 00:06:44.300 align:middle line:84%
What did you create while
you were on this Earth?

00:06:44.300 --> 00:06:46.730 align:middle line:84%
