somebody's life easier?

00:06:46.730 --> 00:06:49.320 align:middle line:84%
Did you demonstrate more
compassion, more love,

00:06:49.320 --> 00:06:50.860 align:middle line:90%
more forgiveness?

00:06:50.860 --> 00:06:53.300 align:middle line:84%
Or was it really
kind of negative,

00:06:53.300 --> 00:06:55.330 align:middle line:84%
where you tried-- you
put out negativity?

00:06:55.330 --> 00:06:56.830 align:middle line:90%
You didn't forgive.

00:06:56.830 --> 00:06:59.360 align:middle line:84%
You could have made someone's
life so much better,

00:06:59.360 --> 00:07:01.230 align:middle line:84%
you could have taken
the higher road,

00:07:01.230 --> 00:07:04.520 align:middle line:84%
but you chose to go down
to the lower levels.

00:07:04.520 --> 00:07:06.160 align:middle line:90%
Right?

00:07:06.160 --> 00:07:10.120 align:middle line:84%
Now that we're all here today
and you're watching this today,

00:07:10.120 --> 00:07:13.060 align:middle line:84%
please take away from
this just a reminder.

00:07:13.060 --> 00:07:16.490 align:middle line:84%
I'm here, honestly,
just to remind you

00:07:16.490 --> 00:07:18.240 align:middle line:90%
