>>VAN PRAAGH: Divine
intervention, right?

00:10:30.965 --> 00:10:31.250 align:middle line:90%
>>AUDIENCE: Right.

00:10:31.250 --> 00:10:33.950 align:middle line:84%
>>VAN PRAAGH: So I believe our
higher self, the creative self,

00:10:33.950 --> 00:10:37.030 align:middle line:84%
the God itself, is
leading us on this path

00:10:37.030 --> 00:10:39.844 align:middle line:84%
we're meant to be because we're
interacting with another soul.

00:10:39.844 --> 00:10:41.510 align:middle line:84%
And we have to learn
something from them

00:10:41.510 --> 00:10:43.830 align:middle line:84%
or teach them or learn
something together.

00:10:43.830 --> 00:10:45.340 align:middle line:90%
That's really what it's about.

00:10:45.340 --> 00:10:48.720 align:middle line:84%
So if there is a person
in your life that you,

00:10:48.720 --> 00:10:52.050 align:middle line:84%
