were misinterpreted.

00:10:52.050 --> 00:10:55.910 align:middle line:84%
Maybe you showed judgment
where you shouldn't have.

00:10:55.910 --> 00:10:57.720 align:middle line:84%
And maybe it's
somebody in the body,

00:10:57.720 --> 00:11:00.140 align:middle line:84%
or maybe it's somebody
