00:11:13.320 --> 00:11:16.010 align:middle line:84%
So they're either in the
body or out of the body.

00:11:16.010 --> 00:11:18.190 align:middle line:84%
Most of us are out
of the body, anyway.

00:11:18.190 --> 00:11:20.000 align:middle line:84%
With just a thought,
we leave the body.

00:11:20.000 --> 00:11:22.330 align:middle line:84%
And just send them a
bit of forgiveness,

00:11:22.330 --> 00:11:24.930 align:middle line:84%
understanding--
maybe as an apology.

00:11:24.930 --> 00:11:27.200 align:middle line:90%
That's fine.

00:11:27.200 --> 00:11:29.460 align:middle line:84%
And the important thing is
as you're sending this out

00:11:29.460 --> 00:11:37.220 align:middle line:84%
to them, I want you
to respect and to feel

00:11:37.220 --> 00:11:40.720 align:middle line:84%
the reaction that
your body gives you.

00:11:40.720 --> 00:11:43.370 align:middle line:84%
When you give out forgiveness,
how does it make you feel?

00:11:43.370 --> 00:11:45.220 align:middle line:90%
And just interpret that.

00:11:45.220 --> 00:11:50.510 align:middle line:90%


00:11:50.510 --> 00:11:52.870 align:middle line:84%
We spend so little
time to forgive others,

00:11:52.870 --> 00:11:56.536 align:middle line:84%
when really that's many
times why we're down here.

00:11:56.536 --> 00:11:57.251 align:middle line:90%
OK.

